"latintype"><anchor xml:id="K_L00380_1" type="commentary"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb31363" subtype="implied"><rs ref="#pmb2713" type="person">Helferich</rs></rs><note xml:id="K_L00380_1h" type="commentary"><bibl><rs ref="#pmb2713" type="person">Hermann Helferich</rs>: <rs ref="#pmb31363" type="work">»Schöne Frauen«</rs>. In: <rs ref="#pmb36340" type="work">Die Zeit</rs>, Bd. 1, Nr. 1, <date>6. 10. 1894</date>, S. 7–8</bibl>.</note></hi> famos; <anchor xml:id="K_L00380_2" type="commentary"/><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Bahr</hi></rs>’s Sachen<note xml:id="K_L00380_2h" type="commentary"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10815">Bahr</rs> hat, unter verschiedenen Namen und Kürzeln, zwei Aufsätze, zwei Buch- und drei Theaterbesprechungen im ersten Heft.</note>, be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>onders <anchor xml:id="K_L00380_3" type="commentary"/><rs ref="#pmb32209" type="work">Burgtheater</rs><note xml:id="K_L00380_3h" type="commentary"><bibl><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Hermann Bahr</rs>: <rs ref="#pmb32209" type="work">Burgtheater</rs>. In: <rs ref="#pmb36340" type="work">Die Zeit</rs>, Bd. 1, Nr. 1, <date>6. 10. 1894</date>, S. 9–10</bibl>.</note> vorzüglich. –</p><p><rs ref="#pmb30397" type="work">Schmetterlings<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlacht</rs> noch nicht ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen, will Freitag gehen. – Schreiben Sie mehr, wann ko<c rendition="#gemination-m"/>en Sie?</p><closer>Herzlichen Gru<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s<space unit="chars" quantity="3"/>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb2121">
